":"3. **共有**","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8150-8d75-cf65ed46c20f","parent":"の3点を併せ持つサービスが、**Notion**なのです。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8161-acc5-e0c64b9bee36","type":"heading_2","parent":"## Notionの使用例","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-811d-a51f-f64275a0e4d7","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-811a-afab-ec2f25a012a4","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- カリキュラム、資料作成","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81c4-aa23-fc553f2dc842","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 授業内容のメモ","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8153-9241-c75b97938331","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 議事録","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81b7-a64f-f757214d47d9","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- タスク管理","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8165-a87c-cbfbbea5b4b0","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 予定表","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81da-a84b-f820731a2892","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 仕様書","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8153-b619-e70247be0e4f","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- ホームページ","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81dd-9e6b-d46ad5d56c35","parent":"**etc…**","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81fb-8f1c-ecf9b426b10c","type":"callout","parent":"> ☝ もちろん、これだけではありません。Notionの持つ可能性は無限大です！","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-812f-b830-dd1912684c9a","type":"heading_2","parent":"## Notionの特徴","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81ae-83c8-d8447006da36","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-81c7-8ee3-f66084cf8d13","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **完全クラウドサービス**","children":[{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-817a-82ea-c29756f42d0e","type":"paragraph","parent":"作業データはリアルタイムにインターネット上のサーバーに保存されるので、セーブ忘れでデータがなくなる心配がありません","children":[]}]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-817d-bba2-ecd23f4439d7","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- **洗練されたレイアウト**","children":[{"blockId":"19c2297